snippet.title: The Flash ZSJL McFarlane Unboxing | Black Widow Reviews | Amber Heard Hate | Boba Fett's Ship Name
snippet.description:
Today I do an unboxing of the McFarlane Snyder Cut Flash figure(Link down below). Talk about the hate Amber Heard is still getting. Talk about those reviews for Black Widow, and how Disney renamed Boba Fett's ship.
